issue.title: Allow a service delegate to create a named service
issue.body: Right now the `#[ServiceDelegate]` Attribute can only be used to create explicit object types. However, we should be able to use this pattern to create _any_ value that might be put into a service; including callables, strings, and other scalar types. If we allow a service to be defined by name and then allow a factory to create that named service it should be able to provide functionality for non-object container values.

release.name: v2.1.0
release.body:
## What's Changed
* Add microseconds to logger timestamps by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/295
* Feature/container analytics stopwatch by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/298
* Update to use annotated-target v0.3 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/299
* Mark configuration as deprecated by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/300
* Task/improve logging composite definition provider by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/301
* Throw appropriate exception if configuration file not found by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/305
* Actually log information with default logger by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/306
* Ensure ContainerAnalyticsObserver respected in configuration by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/307
* Show more useful information when confguration types are invalid by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/308
* Update documentation for 2.1 release by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/320
* Allow bootstrap to explicitly define container factory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/321
* Add changelog entry for bootstrap container factory override by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/322


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/compare/v2.0.0...v2.1.0
